<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.hd-image.com/store/index.php?zenid=5904b399ff6ee7a36f26d91c0935b4ce&amp;main_page=advanced_search_result&amp;search_in_description=1&amp;zenid=5904b399ff6ee7a36f26d91c0935b4ce&amp;keyword=the+awakening" class="external text" title="http://www.hd-image.com/store/index.php?zenid=5904b399ff6ee7a36f26d91c0935b4ce&amp;main_page=advanced_search_result&amp;search_in_description=1&amp;zenid=5904b399ff6ee7a36f26d91c0935b4ce&amp;keyword=the+awakening" rel="nofollow">Skull on a Shelf</a> ("the Aberrant Dreams and HD-IMAGE store"), as linked from <a href="http://aberrantdreams.blogspot.com/2007/11/greetings-everyone-wow-it-has-been.html" class="external text" title="http://aberrantdreams.blogspot.com/2007/11/greetings-everyone-wow-it-has-been.html" rel="nofollow">this Aberrant Dreams news post</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
